rows.label: qst700105_msg0001
rows.name:
We're here to take you home.
Mind coming along?

rows.label: qst700105_msg0101
rows.name: Relax. We mean you no harm.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0201
rows.name:
You must be Ajijii.
Take it easy, you're safe now.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0202
rows.name: Let's get you back to your master, OK?

rows.label: qst700105_msg0301
rows.name: There she is! And looking well, too.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0302
rows.name:
You must be, uh, wossname...
Bhaji...? No, Ajijii, there we go.
Anyway, let's head back.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0401
rows.name:
Ugh, Armus look so dumb with those
big wet eyes...

rows.label: qst700105_msg0402
rows.name:
Right, you're coming with us. Quietly.
Got it?

rows.label: qst700105_msg0501
rows.name: Ah... Ajijii, if I'm not mistaken.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0602
rows.name:
Oh, I'm sorry for startling you.
Shall we head back together?

rows.label: qst700105_msg0702
rows.name:
This game of tag is over.
You're coming home.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0801
rows.name: It heartens me to see you hale.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0802
rows.name:
I'm Wadatsumi, your humble servant.
Let us depart
